OL,3,CAlmost half of people living with MS
OL,4,Cchallenged for using accessible
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,F"Debilitating, exhausting and
OL,8,Funpredictable" - that's the reality of
OL,9,Flife for people living with multiple
OL,10,Fsclerosis in Wales.
OL,12,FOn top of the symptoms of the disease,
OL,13,Fthere's an added challenge; the fear
OL,14,Fof being judged for using accessible
OL,15,Ffacilities.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
