PN,46302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1776874271
OL,3,CAlmost half of people living with MS
OL,4,Cchallenged for using accessible
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,FA new survey by a collaboration of MS
OL,8,Fcharities has shown that almost half
OL,9,F(48%) of people living with the
OL,10,Fcondition in Wales have either been
OL,11,Fchallenged or questioned for using
OL,12,Faccessible facilities, such as blue
OL,13,Fbadge parking spaces, accessible
OL,14,Ftoilets or priority seats on public
OL,15,Ftransport.
OL,17,FOne of those is Gemma Williams. She
OL,18,Fwas diagnosed with MS when she was 21
OL,19,Fyears old.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
