PN,46303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1776874271
OL,3,CAlmost half of people living with MS
OL,4,Cchallenged for using accessible
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,F"I don't look like there's anything
OL,8,Fwrong with me," she said.
OL,10,F"I catch the bus from the station to
OL,11,Fthe hospital each month and sometimes
OL,12,FI have to sit down because my balance
OL,13,For my legs aren't working.
OL,15,F"People don't obviously think I need a
OL,16,Fpriority seat and I have been
OL,17,Fquestioned as to why I've taken it up
OL,18,Fand why I haven't stood up to give it
OL,19,Fto someone else, when in fact I do
OL,20,Fneed it myself.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@OO]rD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1776874271
OL,3,CAlmost half of people living with MS
OL,4,Cchallenged for using accessible
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,F"I've also been challenged when I've
OL,8,Fparked in a disabled bay with my blue
OL,9,Fbadge," she added.
OL,11,F"A woman did question me at a
OL,12,Fsupermarket asking me if I really
OL,13,Fneeded that space when I really did. I
OL,14,Fcan understand why people would think
OL,15,Fthat but it does make it difficult."
OL,17,FTo mark this year's MS Awareness Week
OL,18,Fcampaign, people living with the
OL,19,Fcondition were surveyed to understand
OL,20,Fthe full impact of public judgements.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@GO]sD@AOUwD@dO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
