CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1776874271
OL,3,CAlmost half of people living with MS
OL,4,Cchallenged for using accessible
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,F"We need to raise more awareness and
OL,8,Fthat's what our campaign is all about
OL,9,Fso it's about asking members of the
OL,10,Fpublic to think again, to listen,
OL,11,Flearn and understand what it's like to
OL,12,Flive with MS."
